Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：视觉中国“ 江汉区通报称，鲍某在未告知社区网格员情况下，自建“优惠猪肉蔬菜”团购保障微信群，进行肉、蔬菜、零食等生活物资转卖经营活动，拉小区业主近300人入群，实际参与团购160余人。
Photo Source: Visual China "Jiang Han District reported that without informing community grid workers, Bao set up" preferential pork and vegetable "group to purchase and sell off meat, vegetables, snacks and other living materials, and pulled nearly 300 people into the group, actually participated in the purchase of 160 people.
”针对网传“志愿者”倒卖生活物资赚取差价事件，武汉市江汉区通报称，涉事者并非志愿者，建群团购实为牟利，市场监管部门已对其立案调查。
In response to an incident involving online distribution of "volunteers" selling goods to earn a price difference, Wuhan Jianghan district informed that the participants were not volunteers and that the group purchase was a profit-making enterprise and the market regulator had opened a case against them.
2020年3月15日上午，武汉市江汉区政府办公室官方微博@两江交汇通报称，3月13日，有网民发文称“志愿者倒卖储备肉赚差价”，江汉区新型肺炎疫情防控指挥部对此高度重视，责成汉兴街、市场监管和公安部门迅速进行调查。
On the morning of March 15, 2020, official Weibo @ Shuangjiang, an official Weibo of the Jianghan District Government Office of Wuhan City, reported that on March 13, a netizen wrote that "volunteers resell reserve meat to make a profit difference."
界面新闻注意到，有网友日前在人民网领导留言板栏目给江汉区委书记留言称，其是江汉区汉兴街常远里社区香缇美景小区居民。
Interface News noted that some netizens recently left a message board for the secretary of the JiangHan District, saying that it was a resident of Changyuli District, Hanxing Street, JiangHan District.
政府推出了储备冷冻肉后，该网友加入一个武商爱心肉蔬菜群，群主网名叫：小小的太阳，自称志愿者，“据不完全统计，截止3月11日，群中三百余人，分几次从她那里买了各种生活物资近五万元。
"According to incomplete statistics, as of March 11, more than 300 people in the group had bought nearly 50,000 yuan worth of daily necessities from her in several installments.
”“后来才发现她卖给群友的每一份东西都加了价，比如零食小麻花，中百（超市）售价10.9元，她卖15.9元；有人反映买了3.2斤排骨，收了118元，合36.9元一斤，而政府冷冻排骨定价只有17元一斤。
"" It turned out that everything she sold to her friends was priced at, say, a snack, hemp (supermarket) at 10.9 yuan and she was selling at 15.9 yuan; someone reported buying 3.2 jin of ribs, or 118 yuan (36.9 yuan) a catty, while the government set the price at 17 yuan a pound.
”该网友留言称。
"The netizen message said.
对此，江汉区新型肺炎疫情防控指挥部通报称，经了解，投诉中所称“志愿者”为汉兴街常远里社区香缇美景小区居民鲍某。
In response, the JiangHan District New Pneumonia Command informed that, after understanding, the complaint said "volunteers" for Hanxing Street Changyuan Community Shanti beauty residential area residents.
鲍某自称可以为居民购买平价肉，社区志愿者周某某将其拉进社区组织的团菜群。
Bo said he could buy affordable meat for residents, community volunteer week will be drawn into the community-organized group.
为方便服务居民团购，社区网格员为鲍某发放了志愿者服装，并出具进出小区证明。
To facilitate the purchase of community groups, the community grid for Bao issued volunteer clothing, and issued in and out of the community certificate.
但鲍某在未告知社区网格员情况下，自建“优惠猪肉蔬菜”团购保障微信群，进行肉、蔬菜、零食等生活物资转卖经营活动，拉小区业主近300人入群，实际参与团购160余人。
However, Bao set up a group of "preferential pork and vegetable" groups to sell and sell meat, vegetables and snacks without informing the community grid workers.
3月4日至3月11日，其多次在武商、中百采购肉、蛋、蔬菜等生活物资，加价售卖给小区业主。
From March 4 to March 11, it made numerous purchases of meat, eggs, vegetables and other daily necessities in Wuchang, Zhong100, and sold them to small district owners at a higher price.
通报称，调查中，鲍某承认其并非志愿者，建群团购实为牟利。
The notice said that the investigation, Bao admitted that it is not volunteers, set up a group to buy a profit.
市场监管部门依法责令鲍某立即无条件退还差价给各位参加团购业主，并对其立案调查，将严肃追究其责任。
The market regulator ordered Bob to immediately and unconditionally refund the price difference to the group of owners, and to investigate its case, will be seriously held accountable.
江汉区新型肺炎疫情防控指挥部表示，汉兴街纪工委已约谈常远里社区书记和该网格员。
Jianghan District New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command said the Hanxing Street disciplinary committee has interviewed Changyuanli community secretary and the grid man.
区指挥部要求市场监管部门加大监管力度，严厉打击此类行为；要求全区各街道社区举一反三，严格落实志愿者管理制度，全力服务好居民多样化生活需求，杜绝类似问题再发生。
The District Command requires the market regulator to step up supervision and crack down on such activities. It also requires all the communities in the region to strictly implement the volunteer management system so as to serve the diverse needs of the residents and prevent the recurrence of similar problems.
